# Experimental Logs

This document summarizes all experiments conducted to evaluate the robustness of the **GIT-Large image captioning model** against adversarial attacks and fine-tuning defenses.

- **Model:** microsoft/git-large
- **Training dataset:** Flickr8k
- **Evaluation dataset:** MS-COCO subset (1,000 images)
- **Metrics:** BLEU1-4, METEOR, BERTScore F1

---

# 1. Baseline Model (Pretrained GIT-Large — No Fine-Tuning)

### Model
- Architecture: `microsoft/git-large`
- Training: No additional fine-tuning
- Parameters: ~347M (all frozen)

### Attack Configuration
- FGSM: ε = 8/255, white-box on GIT
- MI-FGSM: ε = 8/255, α = 2/255, 10 iterations, white-box on GIT

